here are some important aspects of claude's website

- Galaxie Copernicus (serif) for large headers — a custom paid font, but we'll use Georgia/ui-serif as the fallback
- Styrene B for the main text input area — we'll substitute with a similar rounded sans-serif
- Tiempo Text for body reading text — we'll use ui-serif/Georgia
- The warm color palette: \#F4F3EE (Pampas/cream background), \#F5F5F0 (off-white), \#1a1a18 (near-black text), \#ae5630 / \#C15F3C (terracotta/orange accent), \#2b2a27 (dark bg)

see how to [[Apply Custom CSS Theme in TiddlyWiki]] and use my [[Claude Flavored Tiddlywiki Theme]]
